snippet.title: Paper Beast - Trailer | PS4, PS VR
snippet.description:
Paper Beast is the new Eric Chahi's game coming to PlayStation VR end 2019.

Somewhere deep down in the vast memory of a data server, an ecosystem has emerged. Decades of lost code and algorithms have accumulated in the eddies and flows of the Internet. A small bubble of life has blossomed. Paper Beast is born.
This trailer uses only real-time footage from the Paper Beast game engine.

https://www.pixelreef.fr/
